snippet.title: On the Peril of Parrots Game - Composer Announcement - "Meta Nuances" composed by Chase Bethea
snippet.description:
This is my announcement video to share that I am the composer of the puzzle game, On the Peril of Parrots developed by SpriteWrench. #videogamecomposer #gamemusic #indiegame 

More about SpriteWrench
https://spritewrench.com/

Wish-list the game -
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2137480/On_the_Peril_of_Parrots/

For more about Chase Bethea check out his website
-http://chasebethea.com

Follow his music on

-Spotify
https://open.spotify.com/artist/4mU9ci0mlYOPZIHHdRqs2g?si=Ga9FcR8hQQKGmxdy8ZClXA

-Tidal
https://tidal.com/browse/artist/22238991
